OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CRoberts
OL,6,FJohn Roberts, Age 100, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 6 November 2023
OL,10,FPart of the Naval offensive on D-Day
OL,11,Fdesigned to counter German artillery,
OL,12,FMr Roberts was a sub-lieutenant aboard
OL,13,Fthe destroyer HMS Serapis.
OL,15,FIt escorted a convoy across the
OL,16,FChannel that included minesweepers
OL,17,Ftasked with clearing the way to Sword
OL,18,FBeach.
