OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CRoberts
OL,6,F"At about half six in the morning I
OL,7,Fsaw for the first time in my life the
OL,8,Fcoast of France," he said.
OL,10,F"And I thought 'this is amazing'. At
OL,11,Fabout seven o'clock a Norwegian ship
OL,12,Fwas torpedoed.
OL,14,F"We were all moving slowly towards the
OL,15,Fcoast and there was this loud
OL,16,Fexplosion.
