OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CRoberts
OL,6,FMr Roberts added: "Three or four days
OL,7,Fafter the invasion, when we had
OL,8,Ffinished bombarding the coast because
OL,9,Fthe Army had moved too far inland, we
OL,10,Fwere protecting all the ships.
OL,12,F"There were about a thousand anchored
OL,13,Foff the coast all disgorging stores
OL,14,Fand goodness knows what.
OL,16,F"But the Germans were coming out every
OL,17,Fnight to attack them. Our job was to
OL,18,Fattack them which we did and they
OL,19,Fdidn't get to the invasion ships at
OL,20,Fall."
