OL,4,CRoberts
OL,6,FSerapis went on to spend several weeks
OL,7,Foffshore.
OL,9,FAlso a veteran of the Arctic convoys,
OL,10,FMr Roberts later flew Sea Fury
OL,11,Ffighters during the Korean War, was a
OL,12,FCaptain of HMS Ark Royal and retired
OL,13,Fas a Rear Admiral.
